  "info": {
    "_postman_id": "ad6da029-807b-4f1e-8a3a-ef699e9e347a",
    "name": "AEME Backend API",
    "description": "Complete test suite for AEME microservices.\n\n**SETUP:**\n1. Start services in order: Eureka (8761) → Auth (8081) → Gateway (8080) → Wearables (8082)\n2. Run any Login request first — tokens are auto-saved to collection variables.\n3. All protected requests use {{accessToken}} automatically.\n\n**Seeded users:**\n- sys.admin / Admin@1234\n- csa.agent / Agent@1234\n- risk.user / Risk@1234\n- mrm.user / Mrm@1234\n- corp.admin / Corp@1234\n- ta.admin / Travel@1234\n- soc.user / Soc@1234",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json",
    "_exporter_id": "55078215",
    "_collection_link": "https://go.postman.co/collection/55078215-ad6da029-807b-4f1e-8a3a-ef699e9e347a?source=collection_link"
  },
